[hassat_female_leader_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Slay Shebbat and all those who would raise their weapons against you. Do not hurt the rest of us, we have no quarel with you.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_female_leader_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Hold your weapon, brave one! I, Abshahe of the great tribe Taerie, beg you to spare our lives. It was our leader, Shebbat, who would force us into battle with humans and other civilized races. Some of us did not cherish his lust for war, but he held the tribe in his iron grip and none of us dared to take action against him. Most of the tribe shared his desire for conquering other sentient races. Now that you have slain him, we are free of his tyranny and can do as we will. Shebbat lead us to war with hassat tribe Guanai. Our tribe was not nearly as strong as their, and we soon had to flee our homeland in the jungle. He ordered us to settle here, raise our youth and hone our skills so that one day we may return and destroy the Guanai. Despite Shebbat's intentions with this place, we began to hold this small piece of land dear. Our only wish is to reside here and raise our kittens in peace. Fighting against the mankind is really not tempting. I beg you to leave us in peace, traveler. We will hunt wild creatures, teach our youth and treat our small land with respect. Any humans passing through here will be granted escort of our hunters. No man will come to harm in our lands. All we ask is to be left alone. And, if you ever run into any of the Guanai, make sure they believe that we are all dead. That would be a huge favor to us.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_female_leader_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Safe travels, the strongest, the bravest and the kindest of humans. May our tribes live in peace and prosperity for long.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_leopard_1_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Last time I spoke with a stranger without permission, Shebbat's henchmen broke three of my fingers.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_leopard_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "You have hunted Shebbat down. I sincerely thank you, human. Many of us only saw him for what he was when he crippled us for slightly upsetting him. He made sure any opposition in the tribe is too weak to confront him.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_leopard_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "If you intend to continue through the cave, you have much greater game to hunt than Shebbat ever could be.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_leopard_2_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Slay Shebbat, adventurer. Make sure his death is slow and painful.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_leopard_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Thank you for taking care of Shebbat, adventurer. I spoke out against him once and he overheard me. He broke my jaw, my left arm and atop of that I've had trouble walking ever since.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_leopard_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I wish the sun was warmer in these parts. Abshahe says we'll get used to local temperature and I believe her, but it does not make it any more pleasant.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_lion_1_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Shebbat is in charge here. Talk to him. I can't help you.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_lion_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "The path from our homeland in jungle has not been easy. Forests were cozy. We climbed the trees, jumped from one tree to another,... Anything that tried to attack us, was quickly clawed to pieces from above. But in plains and icelands we were easy pickings. Furoks, impalers, orthracs... The creatures there were vicious. Only about a third of us made it here. This is the first place where we can exist in relative safety that is out of reach of the Guanai.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_lion_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "It may not be as warm here as it was in the jungle, but we can jump over hills and climb cliffs like no other creatures here. This is a very safe place for us. We could hardly wish for better protected home.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_panther_1_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Shebbat...Deal with Shebbat. Leave me alone.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_panther_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I'm sorry we didn't help you fight Shebbat. He crippled most of us during his rule so that we couldn't rise against him. What strength we had diminished as we were fleeing from the Guanai. Others try to act tough, but don't fall for it. We are extremely exhausted, and will lick our wounds for many years to come.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_panther_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "If you meet the Guanai tribe, tell them you destroyed us all. If they knew some of us still live, they would hunt us to extinction.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_shop_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "You need to speak with out leader, Shebbat.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_shop_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		choice = shop;
		screen_text = "Now that Shebbat is dealt with, we may trade. When we set out on our journey, I realized we would need to establish good relations with our new neighbours wherever we would end up. And what better ways there is than trading? When too parties trade regularly, they form a dependence. Dependence prevents mutual destruction, right? Anyway, I will happily trade with you now. If Shebbat saw me hand you so much as a single chicken bone, he would have both of our heads.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_shop_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		choice = shop;
		screen_text = "Need anything else? Let me see what I can get you.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_tiger_1_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Shebbat won't let us speak with you. As long as he is alive, we cannot help you. Get it?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_tiger_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Thank you, you did it, you little smooth monkey. We were worried his tyranny would never end. Thank you, thank you so much.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_tiger_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Tell your friends from human tribes around here that we are their friends. We are tired of having enemies. We are not like Shebbat and his henchmen.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_tiger_2_beforeleaderiskilled]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Unless Shebbat permits, we may not speak.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_tiger_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "You put Shebbat down. The war is over for us. Never, never again do I want to raise my weapon.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[hassat_tiger_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I love a good hunt, but not war. The purpose of hunt is to eat. The purpose of war is to destroy.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
