	[text*]
	{
		choice = potential_member;
		screen_text = "Hi, neighbour! Can you guess what is going on? Our beloved guard captain is drunk with his entire unit and they are blocking the passage to town. Well, isn't this exactly why I moved to this remote mountain? There may be another route, yes. I once read about a secret cavernal passage to town. You know where the collapsed bridge on the road here is located, right? After it you have to pass two cavernal passages to get here. Well, the secret one should be located somewhere between those two passages. I think it is a favourite gremal mating place thought, so I am not going there to search for something that may not be there by myself. If you want to try, however, I might come along with you. After I escaped trolls at that bridge, my old desire for adventure came back to me. How about I cover your back with my bow?";
